{"tid":1015582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣播道80歲女子割脈自殺 送院治理","createTime":"2019-02-10T06:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T08:51:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"362e4c2589ee3fa3e87f1a742a2f457e4f91bfac","tid":1015582,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"九龍塘廣播道19號龍翔苑8座一個住宅單位，今早(10日)8時57分，一名姓陳(80歲)女子在寓所割脈自殺，幸及時被丈夫發現報警，由救護員到場包紮後，送院治理，警方正調查她割脈原因，案件列作企圖自殺。據悉，有人因病近日備受困擾。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=653e9975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190210/bkn-20190210090907657-0210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190210%2Fbkn-20190210090907657-0210_00822_001.html&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=09e3ddc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190210/bkn-20190210090907657-0210_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"369e8288f2ef2081d4618b260269c463a87e9ac9","tid":1015582,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"咁老"},{"pid":"245c9c88354cc767164b6993a647252322f90a48","tid":1015582,"uid":121546,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"咁大個人自殺前都唔識諗下屋企人會幾傷心，80後真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07dc2ed7690048c38b0c091dd751669d68b584c","tid":1015582,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"245c9c88354cc767164b6993a647252322f90a48","tid":